---
layout: default
title: Newsletter
---

<div class="reading-width main">
	<h1>Newsletter</h1>
	<p>We put out a newsletter approximately once a month to keep our members updated. You can <a href="/newsletter">subscribe to the
			newsletter</a>, or read it on the website!</p>

	<br />
	<hr />
	<br />

	<div class="list">
		{% for article in newsletter %}
		{% if article.published == true %}
		<a href="/newsletter/{{ article.title | slugify }}">Issue {{ forloop.index }} ({{ article.date | date: "%Y %B %d%q" }})</a>
		{% endif %}
		{% endfor %}
	</div>
</div>
